{"tid":2172901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三大女團平均合成臉大比拼","createTime":"2020-08-25T02:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T10:28:54.000Z","uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7abc2a06d5736a508078ec08e17a8223d1c987","tid":2172901,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"近日有網友分享了用app合成的女團平均臉，分別來自SM娛樂的Red Velvet五人、JYP娛樂的TWICE九人、以及YG娛樂的BLACKPINK四人，真的太美啦！<br />\n<br />\n首先是SM的Red Velvet平均臉，臉型和整體布局比較接近Irene的模樣，五官則融合了各個成員的特色，帶著一絲冷豔、一絲孩子氣，嬌美迷人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7EwowZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7EwowZ.jpg&h=67e31c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJYP旗下的TWICE平均臉給人更加活潑開朗的感覺，眼睛圓圓的、卧蠶也比較飽滿，圓鼓鼓的的臉頰和小巧的尖下巴都十分可愛，整體有較強的元氣感：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bHqsYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bHqsYO.jpg&h=2e95a4de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYG的BLACKPINK是另一個路線！眼神高冷、舒展，帶著一種仿彿不經意的、慵懶的情緒，多了幾分成熟和大氣，端正的臉型中和了雙眸神似貓眼的美豔感，一切都切到好處：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjBboxh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjBboxh.jpg&h=676fa1e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d83a225c0eb41183382311948c20b728cca63b56","tid":2172901,"uid":37146,"like":8,"dislike":16,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"TWICE個個根本係MINA加SANA<br />\nBP加左件玫瑰柒左好多<br />\n我諗只係用其他三人會靚到卜街"},{"pid":"a0650dabbbd048c526552234b903204f3b96dbad","tid":2172901,"uid":152432,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83a225c0eb41183382311948c20b728cca63b56","tid":2172901,"uid":37146,"like":8,"dislike":16,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"TWICE個個根本係MINA加SANA<br />\nBP加左件玫瑰柒左好多<br />\n我諗只係用其他三人會靚到卜街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"Twice明明就係子瑜加娜璉<br />\nRose成隊最正好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418f2b83d1f0cf4c93de5bdfe32487d3413d3f27","tid":2172901,"u